  "description": {
    "zh": "我们刚刚接到一名前BEAR的联系，他在前段时间成功逃离了塔科夫。因为他不想再回来跟USEC对抗了，所以这就是派你上场的时候了，毕竟你在这方面是专家，对吧，士兵？任务很简单，击杀一些USEC，在执行任务时假扮扮成他们，并使用一些北约步枪。这样他们会以为是自己人袭击了他们。\n\n对了他还想要你的击杀证明，所以别忘了带上狗牌。\n\n指定装备：\n - Highcom Striker ACHHC IIIA 头盔 （任意颜色款式） 或 Ballistic Armor Co. Bastion头盔 （任意颜色款式） \n - 护甲装备：Highcom Trooper TFO 防弹背心 或 Interceptor OTV防弹衣 或 Eagle Allied Industries MBSS插板胸挂 或 AVS（绿色） 或 IOTV Gen4防弹衣（任意类型） \n - 任何北约制造的突击步枪",
    "en": "We just got contacted by a former BEAR, he managed to get out of Tarkov a while ago. However he doesn't want to get back here to fight the USECs himself, so this is where you come in handy again, after all you are an expert at this, right warrior? The job is simple, take out some USEC operatives, dress like them while you do it and use some western rifles. Just so they think that one of their own guys is fighting them. He also wants proof of your kills so don't forget to take the dogtags with you.\n\nSpecified Gear :\n - A HighCom Striker Helmet / Ballistic Armor Co. Bastion Helmet\n - HighCom Trooper TFO / Interceptor OTV / MBSS / AVS ( Green ) / IOTV Gen4 Body Armors\n - Any Western-Made Assault Rifle"
  },
